Inkundla yaseZimbabwe ikhupha umyalelo wetyala lomntu osebenzela iNY Times ngokuzimeleyo.
Inkundla yaseZimbabwe isichithile isicelo sokukhululwa ngoLwesibini kwityala elijongene nentatheli yeNew York Times.
Intatheli ezimeleyo uJeffrey Moyo utyholwa ngokutyeshela imithetho yokungena kwabantu eZimbabwe xa kutyholwa ukuba wanceda iintatheli ezimbini zamazwe angaphandle ukuba zingene kweli lizwe laMazantsi eAfrika ngokungekho mthethweni kunyaka ophelileyo.
UKathleen Mpofu - elinye lamagqwetha kaMoyo - uthe intatheli izakuvela enkundleni ngomhla wama-28 kuEpreyli.
Umantyi usikhabile isicelo. Ufumanise ukuba urhulumente ukhokele ubungqina obaneleyo ukuba uMnu Moyo aziphendulele kwaye eze kwesi sigqibo, uMpofu uxelele iVOA esuka kwaBulawayo, kuWhatsApp.
“Kukhangeleka ngathi umantyi wayethembele kurhulumente ngobubungqina bamakhadi okutyholwa ngokuba bubuxoki afunyenwe yintatheli yelizwe langaphandle kwaye ngokwendlela atolika ngayo ubungqina obukhokelwa ngurhulumente, wafumanisa ukuba banele ukuba aziphendulele umtyholwa.
Amagqwetha kaMoyo akholelwa ukuba eli tyala lingachithwa, emva kokuba kwa le nkundla inye ekuqaleni kwale nyanga yalikhulula iphephandaba laseZimbabwe.
Igosa lekomishini, u-Thabang Manhika, ngezityholo zokuqhuba iziqinisekiso zomgunyathi kwiintatheli ezimbini zase Mzantsi Afrika ze-New York Times ezingene eZimbabwe zaza zagxothwa kamva.
UMoyo noManhika bebexoxa amatyala abo ngokwahlukeneyo.
Urhulumente waseZimbabwe uthi uMoyo kunye noManhika bobabini bophule imithetho yokufudukela kwelinye ilizwe.
Unobhala osisigxina kwiSebe lezoLwazi uNdabaningi Nick Mangwana uphawule ngesi sigwebo sangoLwesibini.
Sifuna nje ukubona ukuba kukho umthetho nocwangco.
Ukuba umntu wophule umthetho okanye kuyacingelwa, uyakufumana usuku lwakhe enkundleni, ngoko ke ujongene nenkundla, ngoko ke isigqibo asikho sezandleni zethu, sisezandleni zenkqubo zobulungisa kulwaphulo mthetho.
Yindawo yethu leyo,” utshilo uMangwana.
UTabani Moyo weMedia Institute of Southern Africa, okanye iMISA, umemelele ukuba le ntatheli iphathwe ngokufanelekileyo.
“I-MISA Zimbabwe igxininisa isidingo sokuxoxwa kwetyala ngobulungisa. Leyo yindawo esime kuyo lide liphele ityala.
Kuyo yonke into esiyithethayo kukuba naye njengaye nawuphi na ummi, ufanelwe kukufumana ukuxoxa ityala lakhe ngobulungisa,” utshilo uMoyo.
UMoyo, ongummi waseZimbabwe, ujongene neminyaka elishumi entolongweni ukuba ufunyenwe enetyala.
Urhulumente waseZimbabwe uyalele abasebenzi abagonyiweyo ukuba babuyele emsebenzini.
Urhulumente waseZimbabwe uyalele abasebenzi bakarhulumente abathi bagonyelwe i-COVID-19 ukuba bakhawuleze baye emsebenzini emva konyaka besebenza ekhaya, echaza ukwehla kwamanani abantu abanalentsholongwane elizweni.
Abasemagunyeni baphinde babhengeza nabaphi na abasebenzi bakarhulumente abangenabo kobungqina bogonyo baya kuthintelwa kwiindawo zokusebenza kwaye bajongane nesohlwayo, kubandakanya nokumiswa kwemivuzo yabo.
Kwingxelo kule veki, urhulumente kaMongameli uEmmerson Mnangagwa uthe ufuna abasebenzi bakhe baphinde baqalise ukuhlangana ngokobuqu.
Ngorhatya lwangoLwesibini, uMonica Mutsvangwa, umphathiswa wezolwazi welizwe, uthe inani labantu abalaliswe esibhedlele ngenxa ye-COVID-19 liyehla ngokuthe ngcembe.
“Oku kubonisa ukuba amanyathelo okusabela kuzwelonke asungulwe ngurhulumente ayaqhubeka nokuba neziqhamo.
Ngobona ukwehla okuqhubekayo kumanani abantu abosuleleka sisifo sikazwelonke kunye nokufa, kudityaniswa nokwehla kwezinga labo baneziphumo ezimbi kuvavanyo okubonisa ukuba usulelo loluntu lwehlile, zonke iindawo zokungena kufuneka zivulwe kwakhona, kodwa kuqinisekiswe ukuba yonke imiqathango nemiyalelo yokuzikhusela kwiCOVID-19 iyathotyelwa,” utshilo.
Nangona kunjalo, umthetho osisinyanzelo wogonyo awamkelwa ngabo bonke abasebenzi baseburhulumenteni.
Umongameli weAmalgamated Rural Teachers Union of Zimbabwe, uObert Masaraure, uthi abasebenzi bazakuwusa enkundleni lo mcimbi ukuba urhulumente uyanyanzelisa.
“Ikhontrakthi eyasayinwa ngabasebenzi bakarhulumente ayinayo imiqathango yogonyo olunyanzeliswayo.
Ngoko ke ukuba ikomishoni yekonzo zikarhulumente ifuna ukuvalela ngaphandle abasebenzi bakarhulumente abangagonywanga, bophula isivumelwano kwaye oko akwamkelekanga.
Okwesibini, abasebenzi bakarhulumente banelungelo lesidima, banelungelo lokuzikhethela.
Akekho umntu unokunyanzelwa ukuba kufakwe izinto zangaphandle emizimbeni yakhe,” utshilo.
UGqirha Norman Matara, intloko yeZimbabwe Association for Doctors for Human Rights, uthi umbutho wakhe uqaphele ukuba amanye amazwe amaninzi ajonge kugonyo olusisinyanzelo.
Yinto esichasene nayo kakhulu. Sicinga ukuba ukugunyazisa amayeza okugonya yinto ephembelela ukuthandabuza kogonyo.
Ininzi into ethethekayo ejikelezayo xa abantu besithi sinyanzelwa ukuba sigonywe.
Ngokwenene kufuneka sifumane imvume yabantu: sisasaze ulwazi ngogonyo, indlela asebenza ngayo emva koko sikhuthaze abantu ukuba bagonywe kwaye bangabanyanzeli ukuba bagonywe, ”utshilo.
Kodwa uSifiso Ndlovu ophuma kwiZimbabwe Teachers Association uyaluxhasa uluvo lukarhulumente.
Ngokuqinisekileyo, bonke abasebenzi kufuneka bathathe ugonyo.
Hayi ngokuba befuna ukuzikhusela, kodwa bafuna ukukhusela abantu abasebenza nabo emsebenzini.
Ubungqina benzululwazi buthi ukuba ugonywe ngokupheleleyo luza nohlaselo olungephi.
Kutheni ungayithathi loo nto? Akukho nto iphosakeleyo okanye imbi ngayo,” utshilo.
Bamalunga ne-3.3 yezigidi abantu eZimbabwe abaye bafumana izitofu ezimbini ze-COVID-19, ngelixa malunga ne-86,000 befumene isitofu sesithathu.
Uninzi lwabantu baseZimbabwe abavumi ukugonywa, besithi abawathembi amayeza ogonyo eSinopharm kunye neSinovac enziwa eChina..
Iikontraka zomkhosi zabucala zixhasa impembelelo yeRussia eAfrika
Amabhongo e-Russia malunga nezejiyografi kunye nezopolitiko e-Afrika kule minyaka yakutsha nje aye axhaswa ngoonokontraka babucala bazomkhosi, abasoloko bechazwa ngokuba ngamalungu "iWagner" - iqumrhu elingaziwayo ngokwasemthethweni.
Kutshanje, izizwe zaseNtshona zikugxekile ukufika kwamajoni aseRussia kwikomkhulu laseMali iBamako, ibango elaliweyo yiJunta eyathatha amandla okuphatha ngo-2020.
Njenokuba ubudlelwane neFrance busiya busiba mandundu, abalawuli basemkhosini banokuthi bakhangela iindlela zokulungiselela ukuncipha kwenani lemikhosi yaseYurophu ebikade isilwa ukuvukela kweJihadist yaseMali iminyaka.
IiMercs [amajoni] asebenza e-Afrika yinto eqhelekileyo" ngenxa yamashumi eminyaka yokusebenza kweekontraka ezivela eMzantsi Afrika, utshilo uJason Blazakis weqela labacingi iSoufan eliseNew York.
Abantu bakwaWagner bangena kumnyango ekudala uvulelwe uhlobo lwabo,” wongeze watsho.
Akukho lwazi lukhoyo lufumanekayo malunga nobungakanani beliqela okanye ubume bezimali yalo.
Kodwa malunga ne-Afrika, iCenter for Strategic and International Studies (CSIS) eWashington ifumene ubungqina ukususela ngo2016 amajoni aseRassia e-Fortune eSudan, eSouth Sudan, eLibya, kwiCentral African Republic (CAR), iMadagascar kunye neMozambique.
I-Botswana, iBurundi, iChad, iComoros, iDemocratic Republic of Congo, iCongo-Brazzaville, iGuinea, iGuinea-Bissau, iNigeria kunye neZimbabwe nazo zikuluhlu lweCSIS.
E-Afrika "kukho ukuhlangana korhulumento lwamazwe amaninzi , oku kubandakanya iChina," u-Alexey Mukhin weCenter for Political Information eseMoscow utsho njalo kwi-AFP.
Wonke urhulumente unelungelo lokukhusela inzuzo yeshishini lakhe,” wongeze watsho.
iWagner ayikho ngokusemthethweni, kwaye akukho kubhaliswa kwenkampani, iimbuyekezo zerhafu okanye inkcukaca zombutho ezifumanekayo.
Ngethuba i-EU yayifuna ukugweba eliqela ngo-2020, yayijolise kumphathi onamandla waseRussia u-Yevgeny Prigozhin, umlingani kaMongameli u-Vladimir Putin okrokrelwa ngokukhokela iWagner.
Yabeka ezinye izohlwayo ngoDisemba kulo nyaka uphelileyo xa ukufika kwamajoni eMali kubonakala ngokuqinisekileyo - kutyholwa "ukungabina ngqiqo" okuvela eMoscow.
Iingcali zaseNtshona zithi iikontraka zomkhosi zifakwe kwimikhosi esemthethweni yaseRussia njengee-arhente zobuntlola kunye nomkhosi, zinika inkxaso iMosco ngokuyikhanyelela.
Ukuthunyelwa kwabo kumazwe aseAfrika kujolise "ekubeni iRussia ikwazi ukuba... iphinde ifumane elinqanaba lempembelelo" elatshabalala ukuwa kweSoviet Union, utshilo umphandi weCSIS uCatrina Doxsee.
Ubukho bamajoni buya bukhula ngokukhawuleza ukusukela kwingqungquthela yeRussia-Afrika summit yango-2019.
IMoscow ibisebenza “ingakumbi kwindawo ebikade inempembelelo zaseFrance” kwiindawo ezazisakuba yimihlaba yabo ezifana neCAR neMali, utshilo uDjallil Lounnas, umphandi kwiyunivesithi yase-Al Akhawayn yaseMorocco.
Ngelixa iikontraka zomkhosi ngamanye amaxesha zikhulisa ukuthengiswa kwezixhobo zaseRussia, ingeniso "incinci kakhulu xa ithelekiswa nengeniso abakwaziyo ukuyenza kwiimvumelwano zemigodi kunye nokufikelela kwimithombo yendalo," utshilo uDoxsee.
Oko kwenza amazwe angazinzanga aneeminerali okanye ubutyebi be-hydrocarbon abathengi abaphambili - njengaseSyria apho la majoni aqala ukwaziwa kuluntu ngokubanzi.
Kungekho mibuzo ibuzwayo
U-Lounnas uthe enye inzuzo kubathengi kukunqongophala kwengxabano kumalungelo oluntu kunye nedemokhrasi enokuthi ize namaqabane aseNtshona.
IRussia inezinto enomdla kuzo.
Ayibuzi mibuzo, ”wongeze watsho.
Iingxelo zobundlobongela kunye nokuphathwa gadalala aphoi zibonakalisa ukuba inkululeko efanayo inokufikelela kumajoni ngokwawo.
Kwi-CAR, umbutho weZizwe Ezimanyeneyo uphonononga ukubulawa kwabantu abaninzi ngethuba kusebenzisana umkhosi karhulumente kunye namajoni weWagner.
Oyimpimpi yasemkhosini uxelele i-AFP ukuba bangaphezulu kwe-50 abantu ababhubhileyo, abanye " bebulawa emva kokuthyolwa."
NgoLwesine, i-European Union ithe ayizukuphinda iqhubeke noqeqesho lwasemkhosini e-CAR - enqunyanyisiwe ukusukela phakathi kuDisemba - ngaphandle kokuba amajoni elizwe ayeke ukusebenzela iWagner.
Ngeloxesha iziphumo zalamajoni azisoloko zifikelela kumathemba oorhulumente ababaqeshileyo.
E-Libya, amajoni aseRussia afumana ilahleko enkulu kumzamo wonyaka ka-Marshal Khalifa Haftar wokoyisa ikomkhulu i-Tripoli, engazange iphumelele.
Kwaye eMozambique, amaRussia arhoxa ebusweni beqela lama-Jihadists e-Islamic State, ekugqibeleni boyiswa ngabo bakhuphisana noMzantsi Afrika.
Nangona bengenazo izakhono zolwimi kunye namava kule ndawo, iWagner "yachongwa ngenxa yokuba yayiyeyona inexabiso eliphantsi", utshilo uDoxsee.
“Babengenako konke okudingekayo ukuze baphumelele,” wongeze watsho, ephawula ukuba “babenoko ukusilela okumbalwa” kwi-Afrika iphela.
Ukuphumelela ngokupheleleyo kusenokwenzakalisa ishishini labarhwebi, eliqhuba kakuhle kwisiphithiphithi, ungquzulwano kunye nobunzima.
“Ukuba ilizwe elinje ngeCAR libaqeshele ukuqeqesha imikhosi, ukubanceda kwiinzame zabo zomkhosi, kubalukelike ukuba kuyiphumeza oko ukuze baqhubeke nokuqeshwa,” utshilo uDoxsee.
Ukuba ngenene bebengayenza kakuhle ngokwaneleyo ukusombulula impixano, bekungazokubakho sidingo sabo.
INkanyamba uBatsirai Uba buthathaka emva kokubetha iMadagascar, Izantyalantyala zemvula ziyoyikwa
Inkanyamba iBatsirai ibe buthathaka ngobusuku kodwa kusalindeleke ukudama kwamanzi ngenxa yezantyalantyala zemvula emva kokubetha impuma yeMadagascar ngomoya onamandla, iofisi yemozulu yesiqithi yatsho njalo ngeCawe.
“I-Batsirai ibuthathaka,” utshilo uMeteo Madagascar, esongeza ukuba isantya somoya esiphakathi kwalenkanyamba siphantse sehla ukuya kuma-80 kph, ngethuba ezona mvula zivuthuza ngamandla ziye zehla zaya kutsho kwi-110 kph ukusuka kuma-235 aqwalaselweyo xa ifike ngokuhlwa kwangoMgqibelo.
Inkanyamba, isaqhwithi sesibini esihlasele ilizwe elikhulu lesiqithi selwandle iIndian Ocean kwiiveki nje ezimbalwa, sasisiya ngasentshona ngesantya se-19 kph, zatsho iinkonzo zemozulu.
Kodwa "izantyalantyala zemvula okanye iimpuphuma zasekuhlaleni zisoyikwa emva kweemvula ezinkulu," yatsho, isongeza ukuba iBatsirai kulindeleke ukuba ivele elwandle kwijelo laseMozambique kamva ngeCawe.
I-Batsirai yenze ukunkuphuka komhlabal kwisithili saseMananjary, ngaphezulu kweekhilomitha ezingama-530 kumazantsi mpuma we-Antananarivo, malunga ngezithuba zo-8 ngorhatya lexesha lendawo (1700 GMT) ngoMgqibelo.
Ifike kwisiqithi "njengenkanyamba enkulu", ephethe imimoya engama-165 kph, uFaly Aritiana Fabien we-arhente yokulawula iintlekele yelizwe uxelele i-AFP.
I-ofisi yemozulu yelizwe ithe yoyika "umonakalo omkhulu kwaye owndileyo."
Kwiyure nje enesiqingatha emva kokuba ifikile emhlabeni, phantse abantu abangama-27,000 babalwe njengangasenawo makhaya, utshilo uFabien.
Uthe iofisi yakhe ineendawo zokuhlala, ukutya kunye nokhathalelo lwezonyango olulungele amaxhoba, kunye nezicwangciso zokukhangela nokuhlangula ezisele zikhona.
Ingozi enkulu kakhulu'
Inkonzo yemozulu yaseMeteo-France yaxela kwangaphambili ukuba iBatsirai uza kuba "yingozi enkulu" eMadagascar, emva kokudlula eMauritius kwaye yamanzisa isiqithi saseFrance iLa Reunion ngemvula enkulu iintsuku ezimbini.
Kwiiyure ezingaphambi kokuba inkanyamba ifike, abahlali baqubuda bazifika kwelizwe lizihluphekelayo, besachacha kubhubhani wenkanyama iAna ekhupheleni kwenyanga.
Kwidolophu esempuma yonxweme yaseVatomandry, abantu abangaphezu kwama-200 babexinaniselene kwigumbi elinye kwisakhiwo sekonkile samaTshayina.
Iintsapho zazilala kwiimethi okanye koomandlalo.
Inkokeli yabahlali uThierry Louison Leaby ukhale ngokungabikho kwamanzi acocekileyo emva kokuba inkampani esebenza ngamanzi yacima izixhobo ngaphambi kwenkanyamba.
“Abantu bapheka ngamanzi amdaka,” utshilo, phakathi koloyiko lokuqhambuka korhudo.
Ngaphandle izitya zeplastiki kunye nee-emele zazibekwe emgceni ukuze kubanjwe amanzi emvula athontsiza kumacangci ophahla.
“Urhulumente makasincede ngokupheleleyo, akukho kwanto esikhe sayifumana,” utshilo.
Abahlali abakhethe ukuhlala emakhayeni abo babesebenzisa iingxowa zesanti neejeri ezityheli ukuze baqinise uphahla lwabo.
Inkanyamba 'iseyingozi'
Abanye abahlali baseVatomandry babeqokelela izixhobo belungiselela inkanyamba.
“Sineveki siqokelela izixhobo, irayisi kodwa neenkozo kuba ngenxa yokunqanyulwa kombane asikwazi ukugcina inyama okanye intlanzi,” utshilo u-Odette Nirina, oneminyaka engama-65 ubudala waseHolelier eVatomandry.
Ndikwaqokelele namalahle. Apha siyiqhelile inkanyamba, uxelele i-AFP.
Imimoya engaphezulu kwe-50 kph ibethe i-Vatomandry ngentsasa yangoMgqibelo, ihamba nemvula.
I-arhente yeentlekele yathi inkanyamba bekulindeleke ukuba ihlale "iyingozi" njengoko ikhukulise isiqithi esikhulu ngobusuku nasekuseni.
ukudama kwamanzi kulindelekile ngenxa yokuna kwemvula emandla kwimpuma, kumzantsi-mpuma nakumbindi welizwe, ilumkisile.
IZizwe eziManyeneyo zazinyusa ukulungela kwazo ngee-arhente zoncedo, zibeka iinqwelomoya zokuhlangula kwindawo elindileyo kwaye ziqokelela izixhobo zokunceda abantu.
Ubuncinci abantu abayi-131,000 bachaphazeleka nguAna kulo lonke elaseMadagascar ngasekupheleni kukaJanuwari.
Bamalunga nama-60 abantu ababuleweyo, uninzi lwabo kwikomkhulu iAntananarivo.
Lenkanyamba ikwahlasele iMalawi, iMozambique kunye neZimbabwe, yabulala abantu abaninzi.
I-World Food Programme ye-UN yalatha kuqikelelo oluvela kwabasemagunyeni belizwe ukuba abantu abamalunga nama-595,000 banokuchatshazelwa ngokuthe ngqo yiBatsirai, kwaye abongezelweyo abayi-150,000 bangashiyeka bengenamakhaya ngenxa yokudilika komhlaba okutsha kunye nokudama kwamanzi.
Le nkanyamba ibeka engokuzi ubuncinane i-4.4 yezigidi zabantu ngendlela enye okanye enye, i-International Federation ye-Red Cross kunye ne-Red Crescent Societies yathetha yenjenjalo.
Ukunqongophala kwabefundisi bamaKhatholika base-US kuncitshiswe ngabaqeshwa abasuka e-Afrika
Umfundisi uAthanasius Chidi Abanulo - esebenzisa izakhono ezihlonitshiweyo kwilizwe lakhe laseAfrika ukuze alungiselele ngokufanelekileyo emaphandleni ase-Alabama - umisela ixesha elide anokulolula iiholide zakhe zangeCawe ngokusekelwe ekubeni ngubani ohleli ezitulweni.
Imizuzu esixhenxe yeyona ndawo imnandi kuninzi lwamarhamente amhlophe nasele esidla umhlala-phantsi azimase uMthendeleko wolwimi lwesiNgesi e-Immaculate Conception Catholic Church kwidolophu encinci yaseWedowee.
“Ukuba udlulela ngaphaya koko, ulahlekelwa yingqalelo yabantu,” utshilo.
KwiMisa yolwimi lwesiSpanish kwiyure kamva, umfundisi owazalelwa eNigeria - omnye wabefundisi abaninzi baseAfrika okhonza e-US - uyazi ukuba angaliphindaphinda kane ixesha lakhe lokufundisa.
Wathi: “njekokuba esiya eshumayela, kukhona kuba ngcono kubo.
Njengoko esuka kwesinye isikhundla saseMelika esiya kwesinye, u-Abanulo uye wafunda indlela yokwenza ubulungiseleli bakhe obulungele inkcubeko yoluntu alukhonzayo ngelixa efaka umoya welizwe lakhe kwisingqi seMisa.
“Abantu baseNigeria bayakhululeka xa besiza enkonzweni,” utshilo uAbanulo.
“Bayakuthanda ukucula, bayakuthanda ukudanisa.
Inkonzo yonqulo inokuthatha iiyure ezimbini.
Abazikhathazi ngaloo nto.
Ngexesha lakhe leminyaka eli-18 e-US, u-Abanulo uye wathabatha iindima ezahlukeneyo zobufundisi kwilizwe liphela, ebonisa imeko eqhubekayo kwinkonzo yaseMelika yamaKatolika.
Njengoko embalwa amadoda nabasetyhini abazalelwe eMelika abangena kwiiseminari nakwiindawo zoonongendi, iidayosisi zase-US kunye namaziko obuKatolika aguqukele ekufuneni abantu bamanye amazwe ukuze bavale ezo izithuba.
IDiocese of Birmingham, apho uAbanulo ekhokela amarhamente amabini, iye yandisa iphulo layo lokukhangela abefundisi kwiindawo ezinobizo lwenkolo olugqugqisayo njengeNigeria neCameroon, utshilo uBhishophu waseBirmingham uSteven Raica.
Abefundisi baseAfrika nabo babebalulekile kwidayosisi yaseMichigan apho uRaica wayekhonza khona ngaphambili.
“Babeluncedo olukhulu kuthi ukuze sikwazi ukubonelela ngobubanzi nobume bobulungiseleli esinabo kuthi,” utshilo.
IAfrika ngowona mmandla ukhula ngokukhawuleza kwicawa yamaKatolika.
Khona, iiseminari "zigcwele ngokufanelekileyo," watsho uMfundisi.
Thomas Gaunt, umlawuli weGeorgetown University Centre for Applied Research in the Apostolate, eqhuba uphando malunga necawa yamaKatolika enamanani ahlayo.
Kwahlukile e-US apho inkonzo yamaKatolika ijongene nemiqobo ekufuneni abefundisi abakhulele ekhaya emva kwamashumi eminyaka yokuhla kokuya enkonzweni kunye neziphumo ezonakalisayo zokuxhatshazwa kwabefundisi ngokwesondo.
Amabhinqa angamaKatolika namadoda atshatileyo ahlala ethintelwe ekubeni ngababingeleli; Iingxoxo zokuba ukususwa kwezo zithintelo kuya kunciphisa ukunqongophala kwabefundisi azizange zifumane ukuhambela phambili kwiinkokeli eziphezulu zenkolo.
“Into esinayo linani elincinane kakhulu ukuqala kwiminyaka yoo-1970 labantu abangena kwiiseminari okanye kwiinkomfa kwilizwe lonke,” utshilo uGaunt.
Abo bangena ngeminyaka yee-50s kunye nee-60s ngoku sele bekhulile, kwaye ke amanani amiselwa ingakumbi ngokusweleka kwabantu.
Ukususela ku-1970 ukuya ku-2020, inani lababingeleli e-US lehla nge-60%, ngokolwazi olusuka kwiziko laseGeorgetown.
Oku kushiye amarhamente angaphezu kwama-3,500 engenamfundisi ongumhlali. U-Abanulo wongamela amarhamente amabini kumaphandle ase-Alabama.
ICawa yakhe eqhelekileyo iqala ngeMisa yolwimi lwesiNgesi kwi-Holy Family Catholic Church eLanett, malunga neekhilomitha ezingama-200 (125 yemiles) ukusuka eBirmingham ecaleni yemida yelizwe lase-Alabama-Georgia.
