I-US iza kuphelisa ukuvalelwa kwabahambi abasuka kuMazwe asi-8 akuMazantsi e-Afrika
I-US iza kuphakamisa izithintelo zokuhamba ukuya kumazwe asibhozo aseMazantsi e-Afrika ngosuku oluphambi koNyaka oMtsha, i-White House yabhengeza ngoLwesihlanu.
Izithintelo, ezibekwe kwinyanga ephelileyo, zenzelwe ukuphazamisa ukusasazeka kwe-COVID omicron uhlobo olutsha lwesisifo.
Isithintelo somhla wama-29 kaNovemba sithintele phantse bonke abemi abangengabo abase-US ababesandul' ukuhambela eMzantsi Afrika, eBotswana, eZimbabwe, eNamibia, eLesotho, e-Eswatini, eMozambique kunye naseMalawi.
Isithethi se-White House uKevin Munoz uthe kuTwitter ukuba isigqibo sicetyiswe yiCenters for Disease Control and Prevention.
UMunoz uthe izithintelo zokwethutyana malunga nohambo zinike izazinzulu ixesha ebezilidinga lokufunda uhlobo olutsha lwentsholongwane kwaye zigqibe kwelokuba ugonyo olukhoyo luyasebenza ekulweni impembelelo zesisifo.
I-Omicron ngoku isasazeka ngokukhawuleza kulo lonke elase-US, kubandakanywa nabagonyiweyo, kodwa uninzi lwabo balaliswe esibhedlele abagonywanga.
Izithintelo zisinike ixesha lokuqonda i-Omicron kwaye siyazi ukuba amayeza ethu ogonyo akhoyo asebenza ngokuchasene ne-Omicron," utshilo uMunoz kuTwitter.
Uwenza isakhelo ngekamva leeprojekthi zeziseko zophuhliso zaseChina e-Afrika emva kweshumi leminyaka lokuboleka
I-China ixhasa ngezezimali ulwakhiwo lwemizi-mveliso emine yokuphehla umbane ngamalahle kuMazantsi e-Afrika, nangona yayenze isibhambathiso sayo malunga nesimo sezulu ngoSeptemba sokuyeka ukuxhasa oluhlobo lwezeseko zophuhliso phesheya kolwandle.
Kodwa amaziko amatsha aqala ukumila eMzantsi Afrika naseZimbabwe lutyalo-mali olukhulu lwaseBeijing kwizikhululo zeenqwelomoya, imizila kaloliwe kunye nezinye iziseko zelizwe kwilizwekazi lase-Afrika.
Amazwe amaninzi ebelulangazelela utyalo-mali, kodwa ukunyuka kwenqanaba lamatyala kule minyaka mihlanu idlulileyo anyusa ukuthandabuza malunga nethemba lexesha elide leeprojekthi zeziseko ezingundoqo ezisexabisweni eliphezulu.
I-China izibophelele ekubolekeni amazwe ase-Afrika i-153 yeebhiliyoni zeedola ukusuka ngo-2000-2019, kodwa isantya sokuboleka imali sinokucotha.
Izibophelelo zemali-mboleko yaseTshayina zehle ngama-30% ngo-2019 xa kuthelekiswa nonyaka ophelileyo, ngokutsho kweNyathelo loPhando lwaseTshayina-Afrika kwiSikolo seYunivesithi yaseJohns Hopkins yeZifundo eziPhakamileyo zaMazwe ngaMazwe.
Uphando lujonga izibophelelo zemali-mboleko ethi "ihlawulwe kubaboleki njengoko kuphunyezwa iiprojekthi."
Ngokomzekelo, eZambia, abaxhamli bezimali baseTshayina baboleka i-10.3 yeebhiliyoni zeerandi kwimali-mboleko ukususela ngowama-2000 ukuya ku-2010.
I-Uganda ngoku ityala i-China i-200 yezigidi zeedola kwisikhululo seenqwelomoya sayo kuphela, esoyikela ukuba i-China inokusithimba.
Omabini la mazwe ayikhabile intelekelelo kumajelo eendaba ase-Afrika malunga nokuthathwa kweTshayina.
Amanyathelo okubuyisela imali-mboleko Ummelwane waseKenya ufumene imali-mboleko ye-4.5 yeebhiliyoni zeerandi zokwakha uloliwe osuka eNairobi usiya kwisixeko saseMombasa, kwaye iChina ibonisa ukuba iza kuphinda iphinde ilandele imigaqo emva kokuba ikomiti yepalamente yamazwe ase-Afrika ifumanise ukuba ilahleko yokusebenza kunye namatyala kwiibhanki zaseTshayina. ukucinezela abahlawuli berhafu.
Abanye abahlalutyi balumkisile ukuba imiqathango yokuboleka imali e-opaque ithetha ukuba i-China inokubamba iziseko zophuhliso ukuba amazwe ayasokola ukuhlawula.
Amagosa aseMelika kunye neBhritane athi, "amatyala," apho amazwe angenako ukuqokelela imali eyaneleyo yokubuyisela imali mboleko yaseTshayina, acwangciselwe ukunika amandla iBeijing ngokuhamba kwexesha.
Kwinyanga ephelileyo, intloko yeBritish Secret Intelligence Service, uRichard Moore, kudliwano-ndlebe ne-BBC Radio 4 yathi iBeijing inokufumana "amachweba abalulekileyo anokuba ngamaziko omkhosi wamanzi njl njl."
I-Sri Lanka ekuqaleni kwalo nyaka ipasise umthetho abathi abagxeki baya kunika i-China ukulawula izibuko eliphambili lamanzi anzulu elixhaswe yiBeijing.
Kodwa oko akwenzekanga ukuza kuthi ga ngoku e-Afrika, apho oonozakuzaku baseTshayina besala ukubanjwa yinxalenye yeqhinga laseBeijing.
Akukho nanye iprojekthi e-Afrika eyake yahluthwa yi-China ngenxa yokusilela ukuhlawula imali-mboleko yaseChina
Ngokuchasene noko, i-China ixhasa ngokuqinileyo kwaye izimisele ukuqhubeka nemigudu yethu yokuphucula amandla e-Afrika kuphuhliso oluqhutywa ekhaya, "watsho uMzi wozakuzo waseChina eUganda.
Endaweni yokubamba i-asethi, iBeijing inokwandisa ixesha lokuhlawula imali-mboleko okanye imiqathango yokubuyisela kwakhona njengenzala, abahlalutyi baxelele iVOA.
Loo manyathelo anokuthi athintele ukuthathwa kweziseko zophuhliso ngokwawo kwaye agcine isidima samaChina e-Afrika apho urhwebo kunye nokuboleka imali kuye kwagqwesa lowo unamandla amakhulu ngokweedola.
I-China ngokuqinisekileyo iya "kuqhubeka ikhaba itoti ezantsi kwendlela" de ababolekisi bafumane iindlela zokuhlawula imali-mboleko, u-Bulelani Jili, ongumfundi wase-Afrika we-Ph.D. umviwa kwiYunivesithi yaseHarvard, uxelele iVOA.
Ukuthimba nayiphi na impahla, kubandakanya nezimbiwa, "kuya kuqinisekisa ukuthambekela kwabantu baseChina njengomdlali we-neocolonial," utshilo uJili, kunye nomngcipheko wokuphazamisa ubudlelwane bezozakuzo "nabanye babahlobo abambalwa i-China enabo kwihlabathi."
Ukusuka kwicala laseChina, malunga nokufikelela kwiimarike ezintsha ezinokwenzeka kunye nokwandisa imisebenzi yoqoqosho - kunye nobudlelwane bozakuzo, utshilo.
Iinkxalabo zemali-mboleko yaseChina
I-China ikhuthaza ukuboleka imali kwi-Afrika ekufuneni imbuyekezo ephezulu kutyalo-mali kunye nodumo lwehlabathi jikelele njengomxhasi wamazwe ahluphekileyo, utshilo u-Edward Miguel, unjingalwazi we-Oxfam kwi-Environmental Resource Economics kwiYunivesithi yaseCalifornia, eBerkeley.
Izama "ukulingana ne-U.S." njengelizwe elinikelayo, watsho.
Nangona kunjalo, iTshayina yohlukile kwabanye ababolekisi bamazwe ngamazwe kunye nabaxhasi ikakhulu ngenxa yokungafihli nto okubangela imibuzo e-Afrika kunye naseNtshona, uMiguel ukholelwa ukuba.
Ngokungafaniyo nemali-mboleko evela koorhulumente basentshona okanye imibutho ebolekisa ngemali yamazwe ngamazwe njengeBhanki yeHlabathi, efuna ukukhuselwa kwabasebenzi kunye nokusingqongileyo kwiiprojekthi ezixhaswa ngemali, uncedo lwaseChina kunye neemali-mboleko e-Afrika ziye zachazwa ngokuthi "akukho ntambo ziqhotyoshelweyo," eziye zanomtsalane kumazwe amaninzi.
Kodwa amazwe ase-Afrika, ngakumbi uqoqosho luluhle ngenxa yeempembelelo ze-COVID-19, ajongene nengxaki eyandayo yokuhlawula imali mboleko, utshilo uHannah Ryder, ugxa omkhulu kwiNkqubo yeAfrika kwiziko lokucinga lase-US leSifundo seQhinga kunye neHlabathi.
I-China kunye namanye amazwe aya ephucuka ngakumbi ekuxoxweni omnye nomnye, wabhala uDeborah Brautigam weSikolo se-Advanced International Studies kwiYunivesithi yaseJohns Hopkins kunye neHarvard Business School's Meg Rithmire kwinqaku elidibeneyo.
Abahlali baseDakar, eSenegal, apho i-500-personment Forum ye-China-Africa Cooperation yenzeke ngoNovemba 29-30, bafuna iziseko ezingakumbi ezixhaswa ngemali yaseTshayina kodwa ngaphandle kwamanqanaba etyala njengalawo e-1990, uRyder waphawula.
Ababolekisi baseTshayina kulindeleke ukuba baboleke imali encinci e-Afrika ukuya phambili kwaye bahlalutye ngononophelo ngakumbi iiprojekthi ezixhasa inkxaso-mali, iingcali zithi. Iimali-mboleko sele "zithobile" [zicinywe] ukusuka kwincopho ngo-2014, utshilo uJili.
Izibophelelo ngemali-mboleko kunye nolunye utyalo-mali olwenziwe kwintlanganiso yeNtsebenziswano ye-China ne-Afrika lufike kwiibhiliyoni ezingama-40 zeerandi, isinye esithathwini esingaphantsi kweebhiliyoni ezingama-60 zeerandi ezenziwe kwinkomfa enye ngowama-2018.
Ababolekisi banokulinganisa imali mboleko ngokusekwe kuqikelelo lwekamva lobhubhane xa amazwe ase-Afrika enemali eninzi, utshilo uYun Sun, umlawuli wenkqubo yaseMpuma Asia kwiziko iStimson eWashington.
Enye inketho, uthe, kukuqinisekisa ukulingana kwamaTshayina kwiiprojekthi ezizayo njengembuyekezo yemali mboleko endala, utshilo kudliwanondlebe lweVOA.
Iyingozi kwezopolitiko, kuba nangona ingelulo utshintshiselwano lwe-asethi, inuka kakhulu njengokutshintshana, kwaye [ukuba] i-China ixhaphaza isikhundla esibuthathaka saseAfrika, ngoko andicingi ukuba kuya kwenzeka kwixesha elizayo kwaye enyanisweni. olu hlengahlengiso lwetyala luthatha ixesha,” utshilo uSun.
I-China iya isiba nokuzithemba ngakumbi ngalo lonke eli xesha ekusekeni intsebenziswano phakathi kwamashishini abucala namazwe ngamazwe, nangona amazwe amaninzi ase-Afrika esaxhalabile malunga nokuphindaphinda ingxaki yamatyala ngeminyaka yoo-1980 noo-1990 xa amazwe ayengakwazi ukuhlawula amatyala, utshilo uRyder kwingxelo yoShishino lwase-Afrika. .
Imibutho yezizwe ngezizwe ekugqibeleni yalicima elatyala elingafikelelekiyo ngeemeko ezibandakanya ukuvula "uqoqosho lwabo kurhwebo lwamazwe ngamazwe, ukukhulula iimali zabo kunye nokunciphisa kakhulu iindleko.
ukutshintshiselana ngemali-mboleko,” wabhala uPeter Fabricius kwiZiko leZifundo zoKhuseleko.
Ukukhawuleza ukuza ngoku, kunye nemali-mboleko evela e-China, amazwe ase-Afrika, uMiguel uthe, bahlala bebuza ukuba "sivumelene ukwenza ntoni" kwaye "sityala malini" e-China.
IDutch yenza uvavanyo lohlobo olutsha lwesisifo emva kokufumana abantu abangama-61 abane-COVID phakathi kwabakhweli boMzantsi Afrika.
Abasemagunyeni kwezempilo baseDutch bathi ngoMgqibelo bafumene abantu abayi-61 abanesifo se-COVID-19 phakathi kwabantu ababhabhe ngenqwelomoya ngolweSihlanu besuka eMzantsi Afrika kwaye ngoku besenza olunye uvavanyo ukubona ukuba ingaba bakho na abosulelwe luhlobo olutsha lwesifo i-omicron.
Ezizigulane zifunyanwe phakathi kwabakhweli abamalunga nama-600 abafike kwisikhululo seenqwelomoya i-Amsterdam Schiphol ngeenqwelomoya ezimbini ngolweSihlanu phambi kokuba urhulumente waseDutch amise iinqwelo moya ezisuka emazantsi eAfrika ngenxa yenkxalabo malunga nohlobo olutsha lwesisifo.
Abaphathi bezempilo baseDutch bathi ngoMgqibelo bazakufuna ukunxibelelana nabahambi abafike bevela eMzantsi Afrika, eBotswana, e-Eswatini, eLesotho, eMozambique, eNamibia kunye naseZimbabwe ukusukela ngoMvulo kwaye babakhuthaze ukuba bathathe uvavanyo ngokukhawulezileyo.
Abakhweli abavela kwiinqwelomoya zangoLwesihlanu bagcinwe bohlukene nabanye abahambi kwaye abo bafunyaniswe benaso esisifo bagcinwe bodwa kwihotele ekufutshane nesikhululo seenqwelomoya.
Isithethi senkonzo yezempilo sithe ayizukwaziwa de kube nguMgqibelo ukuba ingaba kukhona na abakhweli abosulelekileyo kolu hlobo lutsha lwesisifo.
Isithethi se-KLM, ingalo yaseDutch ye-Air France, ithe inkampani yeenqwelomoya ibizama ukufumanisa ukuba yeyiphi na imigaqo ekhoyo ukusukela ngentsasa yangoLwesihlanu ukuthintela abantu abosulelekileyo yi-COVID-19 ukuba bakhwele kwiinqwelomoya, ezisuka eKapa kunye naseRhawutini.
Imithetho kwiwebhusayithi yenkampani yathi abakhweli kufuneka baveze iziphumo zovavanyo lwe-COVID-19 iziphumo "zerapid antigen" ethathwe kwiiyure ezingama-24 ngaphambi kokuhamba kodwa bekungafuneki ukuba babonise ubungqina bogonyo.
Iyamangalisa ngokwenene' uPaula Zimmerman, umfoti waseDutch ubuye kutyelelo losapho lwakhe eMzantsi Afrika ngentsasa yangoLwesihlanu, uthe imeko yabakhweli kwiinqwelomoya yayinesiphithiphithi, njengoko babegcinwe belindile kwindlela yeenqwelomoya nakwisikhululo sazo iiyure.
UZimmerman waxelelwa ukuba ufunyaniswe engenaso esisifo ngentsimbi yesi-4 kusasa, phantse kwiiyure ezili-18 emva kokufika e-Amsterdam, kodwa wathi emva koko wafumanisa ukuba wayemi ecaleni kwendoda eyayisazi ukuba yona inaso esisifo.
“Yayingummangaliso ngokwenene.
Kwakungekho kulungelelaniswa.
Kwakukho abantu abambalwa kwaye kungekho mntu ulawulayo."
Emveni kokuchitha iiyure kwinqwelomoya ekusenokwenzeka ukuba inabakhweli abaninzi abosulelekileyo kwenza uZimmerman wanexhala iintsuku, utshilo.
“Ndixelelwe ukuba balindele ukuba baninzi abantu abaza kufunyanwa banaso esisifo emva kweentsuku ezintlanu.
Inendawo eyothusayo into yokuba ubukwinqwelomoya enabantu abaninzi abafunyaniswe ukuba banaso esisifo.”
Ukuvalwa kwenqwelomoya zaseDutch akuthethi ukuba zonke iinqwelomoya ezisuka eMazantsi e-Afrika zisiya eNetherlands ziyanqunyanyiswa, njengoko abemi baseDutchi bevumelekile ukuba babuyele ekhaya, ngelixa abemi be-EU bevumelekile ukuba bangene kumazwe abo.
Abasebenzi bezempilo, abasebenzi beenqwelo moya kunye nabantu abanezidingo ezicinezelayo basavumelekile ukuba bahambe.
I-KLM iya kuqhubekeka ineenqwelomoya eziya kulo mmandla, kodwa abahambi kunyanzelekile ukuba bahlale bodwa kangangeentsuku ezintlanu xa befika eNetherlands.
Uhlobo olutsha lwesisifo lufunyaniswe ngethuba amazwe amaninzi aseYurophu exakene nokwenyuka kwamanani abantu abane-coronavirus.
NgoLwesihlanu urhulumente waseDutch ubhengeze ukuvalwa ebusuku kweebhari, iivenkile zokutyela kunye neevenkile ezininzi njengoko ezama ukunqanda irekhodi elophula irekhodi lwabantu abanesifo i-COVID-19 egxobha inkqubo yakhe yezempilo.
I-EU iyakunqumamisa ukuhanjelwa ngabantu abasuka eMazantsi e-Afrika ngenxa ye-COVID entsha eyahlukileyo
Amazwe e-European Union avumile ukumisa ukuhanjelwa ngabantu abasuka kuMazantsi e-Afrika emva kokubhaqwa kolunye uhlobo olutsha lwe-COVID-19, umongameli we-EU uthethe wenjenjalo ngoLwesihlanu.
Ikomiti yeengcali zezempilo ezisuka kuwo onke amazwe angama-27 e-EU "avumelene ngesidingo sokubeka ikhefu likaxakeka kwaye abeke uthintelo lwexeshana lokumisa konke ukuhamba okuya e-EU kusuka eMazantsi e-Afrika," utshilo umongameli waseSlovenia we-EU kuTwitter.
Izithintelo zimiselwe iBotswana, iEswatini, iLesotho, iMozambique, iNamibia, iMzantsi Afrika kunye neZimbabwe, satsho isithethi seEuropean Commission uEric Mamer ku-Twitter.
Igosa le-EU lathi oorhulumente be-EU baye bacelwa ukuba bangakukhuthazi ukuya kula mazwe.
Ilizwe ngalinye kumazwe angama-27 e-EU likhululekile ukusebenzisa imilinganiselo emitsha ngokuthanda kwalo. Amanye sele ebesebenzisa imiqathango.
Amagosa e-EU athi akukabikho sigqibo senziweyo malunga namanye amazwe akwezinye iindawo zehlabathi apho kufunyenwe khona oluhlobo lwesisifo, amazwe aquka iHong Kong, Israel kunye neBelgium, ilizwe le-EU.
