I-Italy ibeka umthetho wokuvalwa kwayo kubantu abasuka kwamazwe asibhozo akuMazantsi e-Afrika
I-Italy ibeke uthetho wokuvalwa kwayo ngolwesiHlanu kubantu abakhe bandwendwela naliphi na ilizwe kumazwe asibhozo aseMazantsi e-Afrika kwezi ntsuku zili-14 zidlulileyo, ngenxa yokusasazeka kodidi olutsha lwe-COVID-19 khona.
Umphathiswa wezempilo e-Italy uRoberto Speranza utyikitye umyalelo olawulayo wokuvalelwa kwabahambi abavela eMzantsi Afrika, eLesotho, eBotswana, eMalawi, eZimbabwe, eMozambique, eNamibia nase-Eswatini.
“Iinzululwazi zethu zifunda uhlobo olutsha lwe-B.1.1.529.
Okwangalomzuzu, siza kuthatha esona silumkiso sibalaseleyo,”utshilo uSperanza.
Iingcali zokusingqongileyo zaseZimbabwe zifuna ngaphezulu malunga nentetho ngoTshintsho lweMozulu
Iingcali zokusingqungileyo eZimbabwe ziphendule ngomsindo kwintetho kaMongameli uEmmerson Mnangagwa kwinkomfa ye-COP26, apho athembise ngokulwa kukarhulumente wakhe esilwela ngokuchaseneyo nokugawulwa kwamahlathi kunye nokutshintsha kwemozulu.
Iingcali zokusingqungileyo zithi urhulumente uxakekile enikezela ngomhlaba kwiinkampani, ingakumbi ezamaTshayina, ukuba zembe amalahle ukuze zisebenzise amandla, nto leyo i-COP26 ifuna apheliswe.
NgoLwesibini eSkotlani, uMongameli uEmmerson Mnangagwa uthethe kwiNkomfa yeZizwe eziManyeneyo yoTshintsho lweMozulu ka-2021, eyaziwa ngokuba yiCOP26, apho ebongoze amazwe aphuhlileyo ukuba ahlawule ngokubangela ukufudumala kwehlabathi ngokukhupha iigesi emoyeni.
Uthe amazwe asaphuhlayo afana neZimbabwe ahlawula iziphumo zoko kukhutshwa komoya ongcolileyo.
Ukwathembise ngentsebenziswano lelizwe lakhe kumlo ochasene nokutshintsha kwemozulu.
“IZimbabwe iye yalihlaziya igalelo layo elimiselwe kuzwelonke, ukuzimisela okunemiqathango engama-40% ngomntu ngamnye ekujoliswe ekunciphiseni kokukhutshwa kwegesi engcolisayo ngo-2030.
Amaqhinga abanzi ayaphunyezwa ekumiseleni uhlengahlengiso lokutshintsha kwemozulu kunye nokomelela kuwo onke amacandelo oqoqosho lwethu, utshilo uMnangagwa.
Oku kuvele kanye xa iingcaki zokusingqungileyo eZimbabwe zicela urhulumente ukuba arhoxise iphepha-mvume lokuhlola elinikwe inkampani yase China ukuba imbe amalahle ukuze isebenzise amandla awo.
Iziko loLawulo lweMithombo yeNdalo ngomnye wemibutho ephikisana nokunikezelwa kweli phepha-mvume.
Eli qela likhuthaza amandla ohlaza, kwaye liloyiko lokuba ukusetyenziswa kwamalahle kubangela ukutshatyalaliswa kwamahlathi okugqithisileyo.
UHenry Nyapokoto, umphathi wenkqubo yeli qela, uthe izimvo zikaMnangagwa zihamba ngokuchasene noko akubona kusenzeka.
“Kodwa urhulumente ebekwimo esebenza ngokugqithisileyo ukukhuthaza imigodi kuyo yonke indawo ukuze kufikelelwe kuqoqosho lwemigodi yeebhiliyoni eziyi-12 zeedola.
Kunjalo nje, ayenzi ngqiqo yendalo ukuba iZimbabwe ifumane uqoqosho lweedola ezili-12 leebhiliyoni ezisekelwe kwiindlela ezimbi zemveliso, ukusetyenziswa okungalunganga, okushiya kusetyesiswe indawo enkulu yendalo okanye ilifa lentlekele yendalo.
Sonke siyaqonda ukuba imigodi iza nokutshatyalaliswa kwamahlathi asebenza njengendawo yokucoca umoya nendawo apho izilwanyana zasendle zihlala khona,” utshilo uNyapokoto.
UNyapokoto wongeze wathi iZimbabwe ihlola ioyile negesi kumda wayo osemntla-mpuma neZambia, enye yezinto enokukhokelela ekutshatyalalisweni kwamahlathi.
Ngaphandle kwempembelelo yeoyile kunye negesi kukufudumala kwehlabathi, kuza kubakho (a) isiphumo esicacileyo, esithe ngqo sale migodi yeoli kunye negesi kuluntu okanye kwinqkubo yendalo.
Umhlaba uya kucocwa ukwenzela imigodi nezinye iziseko zophuhliso eziza kuxhasa loo migodi.
Oku kuchasene nokwenza luhlaza uqoqosho abathetha ngalo eGlasgow,” utshilo uNyapokoto.
Uthe iZimbabwe ikwishumi lamazwe aphambili ekutshatyalalwisweni kwamahlathi, malunga neehektare ezingama-300,000 zamahlathi ezithi zigawulwe ngonyaka.
Kodwa uByron Zamasiya weZimbabwe Environmental Law Association uthi uMnangagwa wayenyanisekile kwintetho yakhe yeCOP26 malunga nokulwa ukugawulwa kwamahlathi okubangelwa sisidingo sokusebenzisa amandla ombane.
“Kungoko ke, umba wokulwa ukutshatyalaliswa kwamahlathi yeyona nto iphambili ekufuneka inikwe iingqwalasela malunga nokukhutshwa kwegreenhouse gas eZimbabwe.
Imithi isebenza njengendawo yokucoca umoya njengoko ifunxa icarbon dioxide, eyona nto ingunobangela wokufudumala kwehlabathi.
Into esinokuyifuna njengelizwe kukufumana eminye imithombo yamandla ombane ekhoyo, ingakumbi kuluntu lwasemaphandleni oluthembele kumafutha eenkuni kwaye olunenxalenye enkulu ekugawuleni imithi.
