IRed Cross: ngabantu abangama-48,000 akuqinisekiweyo ukuba balahlekile kwi-Afrika jikelele.
I-International Committee ye-Red Cross ithi bangaphezu kwe-48,000 abantu abalahlekileyo kwi-Afrika iphela, kwaye ubuncinane abayi-21,600 ngabantwana.
Uninzi lwababhalisiweyo abanyamaleleyo - okukholelwa ngokubanzi ukuba liqhezu lelizwekazi elibanzi, intlekele yobuntu engabhalwanga - inxulunyaniswe nongquzulwano oluxhobileyo, ubundlobongela, iintlekele kunye nokufudukela kwilizwekazi liphela.
I-International Committee yombutho weRed Cross ithi liyanda inani labantu abaza phambili bazokuxela abantu abalahlekileyo eAfrika jikelele.
U-Amaya Fernandez, ongumcebisi wemibutho yoluntu lwabalahlekileyo kunye neentsapho zabo eNtshona Afrika, uthi unobangela wokunyuka kwamanani kuphindwe kabini.
“Kwesinye isandla, kungenxa yokuba sizama ukubhalisa amatyala abantu abalahlekileyo mmandla uphel.
Kodwa kwakhona, ngokuqinisekileyo, kungenxa yokuba kwande undlobongela kunye nongquzulwano olufunyenwe kwilizwekazi, kwangaxeshanye lunyusa amathuba okuba abantu balahleke umphelo.
Xa kujongwa amanani ethu, phantse isiqingatha sabantu abalahlekileyo ngabantwana abancinci kwaye uninzi lwabo ngamadoda.
Phakathi kwabantu ababhinqileyo...siyabona ukuba uninzi ngabantwana, utshilo.
Ukufunyanwa kwe-ICRC kubonisa ukuba abantu abayi 39,360 abalahlekileyo kubantu abayi-48,000 bavela kumazwe asixhenxe aneengxabano ezixhobileyo.
Ngokutsho kweStockholm International Peace and Research Institute, amazwe angama-20 aseAfrika anongquzulwano ngezixhobo.
Kumazwe angama-20, ali-10 abona ungquzulwano oluqatha.
UFernandez uthi ungquzulwano oluqhubekayo kumazwe athile eAfrika lubangele intlungu engakumbi kunye nokubandezeleka kwiintsapho zabo abalahlekileyo.
Iziphumo zobuntu... ezibangelwa lungquzulwano oluxhobileyo oluthatha ixesha elide luhlala lubonakala kudliwano-ndlebe.
Umzekelo, isiqingatha seentsapho ezifumane udliwano-ndlebe eNigeria zaxela ukuba izalamane zabo zilahlekile ngo-2014-2015.
E-South Sudan, uninzi lwezizalwane bezikhangela abantu abalahlekileyo phakathi kweminyaka u-2013 no-2016.
E-Libya, izizalwane zitshilo ukuba zikhangela izalamane zazo ezilahlekileyo ukusukela kwiminyaka yoo-70 ukuzokuthi ga ngoku, kwaye kuyafana ngokunjalo kwabo base-Ethiopia nase-Uganda,”utshilo.
Ezinye iingcaphephe zibona kunyanzelekile ukuba kuqeqeshwe abasebenzi basekuhlaleni kunye nee-arhente zokhuseleko malunga nokubaluleka kokwabelana ngolwazi ukunceda ukufumana abantu abalahlekileyo.
Umncedisi womkomishinala wamapolisa eZimbabwe uCrispen Lifa uthi ilizwe lakhe kunye nommandla badinga inkqubo yolawulo lolwazi ukuze kulandelelwe amatyala abantu abadukileyo.
“Kukho isidingo sokuba kubekho uvimba weenkcukacha ekufuneka uhlaziywa ngalo lonke ixesha ukuze bonke abantu abalahlekileyo, kwanabo bangasekhoyo... bafakwe kwiziko ledatha kwizikhululo zamapolisa.
Ekugqibeleni, olo lwazi kunyanzelekile ukuba lubekwe endaweni... ngoko ukuba ufuna ukujonga kwilizwe liphela inani labantu abalahlekileyo, uyakulufumana ngokukhawulezileyo ulwazi kwindawo ephakathi, utshilo.
Umninawa kaFauziya Hussein walahleka ngoJuni emva kokukhululwa yinkundla yaseKenya.
Le ndoda ineminyaka engama-39, utyholwa ngemiba edibene nobunqolobi, kodwa inkundla yamfumana engenatyala yaze yayalela ukuba akhululwe ngamapolisa.
Udadewabo, uFauziya Hussein, uthi abaphendanga bambona.
Ndiyayazi ukuba basambambile. Ngalo lonke ixesha awayevalelwe ngalo, umnakwethu wazinika ixesha lokufowuna. Wafowunela umama.
Ngoko ukuba bamkhulula kutheni engamfowuneli umama?
Ngoko, ndiyazi ukuba azange bamkhulule, utshilo.
NgokukaHussein, amapolisa amxelela ukuba amkhulule umnakwabo.
I-ICRC icela oorhulumente baseAfrika ukuba bancede banqande ukunyamalala kwabantu ngokuthu kukhangelwe, kuchongwe, kwaye kujongwe iimfuno zeentsapho ezilahlekelweyo.
