UBolt uphumelele izihloko ezithathu ezithe ngqo eBeijing ngo-2008 kwaye umhlala-phantsi wakhe ngo-2017 ushiye umngxuma kumsitho weembaleki, kungekho mntu unyukayo ukuzalisa izihlangu zaseJamaica.
NgoMgqibelo, phakathi kwamaqondo obushushu angaphezulu ku-30, iimbaleki zangena ebaleni njengoko ziqala iinzame zokuphumelela uBolt ophethe irekhodi yehlabathi.
