UZuma woMzantsi Afrika uzakuqhuba uTshutshiso lwaBucala ngakuMtshutshisi
Owayesakuba ngumongameli weli loMzantsi Afrika uJacob Zuma uqhuba iinkqubo zokutshutshisa ukususa umtshutshisi okhokelayo kwityala lobuqhophololo emva kokungaphumeleli kwezomthetho, isiseko sakhe satsho ngeCawe.
Kwinyanga ephelileyo iNkundla ePhakamileyo yeziBheno (SCA) yasikhaba isicelo sikaZuma sokuba umtshutshisi okhokelayo uBilly Downer alishenxise eli tyala emva kokumtyhola ngokukheth’ icala kunye nokupapasha ulwazi oluyimfihlo kwintatheli ngokuchasene nomthetho wesizwe wotshutshiso, phakathi kwezinye izikhalazo.
I-SCA isikhabile isicelo semvume yokubhena ngesizathu sokuba akukho themba libambekayo lokuphumelela kwaye asikho esinye isizathu esibambekayo sokuba kutheni isibheno kufuneka simanyelwe.
Isithethi seJacob Zuma Foundation, uMzwanele Manyi, uxelele indibano yonondaba ukuba imiyalelo kaZuma kwiqela lakhe lezomthetho ukuba liqalise ukutshutshisa labucala “iza kuqala ukusebenza kwezi ntsuku zimbalwa zizayo.
Ukwathe igqiza lamagqwetha kaZuma lifake isicelo sokuphinda siqwalaselwe kumongameli weSCA, uxwebhu lwezikhalazo zokumamela isibheno.
UZuma, owagxothwayo kumbutho olawulayo we-African National Congress ngo-2018 emva kweminyaka engamashumi amabini engumongameli, uzikhanyelanga izityholo zobuqhophololo, ukurhwaphiliza imali kunye norhwaphilizo kwityala ekudala ligquba malunga nesivumelwano sezixhobo ezixabisa iibhiliyoni ezimbini zeerandi kwiminyaka yoo-1990.
Ityala lesivumelwano limphethe kakubi uZuma ukusukela oko wagxothwa njengosekela mongameli welizwe ngo-2005. Wathi wayelixhoba lokuzingelwa kwamagqwirha kwezopolitiko.
NgoMvulo lo ukuxoxwa kwetyala okusele kulibazisile kuzokuqala kwaye uZuma uzakube ekhona enkundleni.
UManyi uthe uZuma, nogqiba iminyaka engamashumi asibhozo ubudala ngoLwesibini, ufaka isicelo sokumiswa ngenxa yokuba “kucace gca ukuba iimeko zokuxoxwa kwetyala ngokufanelekileyo azikho.
NgoMvulo iqela lakhe liza kuphendula kwakhona kwingxelo efungelweyo eyongeziweyo enikwe nguGunyaziwe woTshutshiso weSizwe apho bafuna ukwazisa ubungqina obutsha kwityala.
“Eyona nto ifunwa nguMongameli uZuma yimini yakhe enkundleni, kuxoxwe ngokungenamkhethe hayi kwiqonga eliqhathwa nguRhulumente,” utshilo uManyi.
UBume boMzantsi Afrika bokungathathi cala kwiRussia bubeka umngcipheko wobudlelwane babazwe ngamazwe: abahlalutyi
Umongameli woMzantsi Afrika uCyril Ramaphosa ngoMvulo ukhusele ukungathabathi cala kwakhe kuhlaselo lwase-Ukraine yiRussia, ememelela iingxoxo- hayi ukugxeka.
Abagxeki baye bagxeka urhulumente ngokusilela ukuxhasa iUkraine ngokuchasene nommelwane wayo.
Abahlalutyi bathi uMzantsi Afrika uvumela ubudlelwane bezopolitiko nezoqoqosho neMoscow bubeke emngciphekweni ubudlelwane nehlabathi liphela.
Uthethathethwano endaweni yezixhobo okanye uxinzelelo lwezoqoqosho yindlela uRamaphosa angathanda ukuyibona isetyenziselwa ukulungisa impixano yaseRussia-neUkraine.
Ukungaguquguquki kukaRamaphosa kwasikhaba isicelo sangaphambili sesebe lezobudlelwane bezizwe ngezizwe sokuba iRussia mayirhoxise imikhosi yayo.
ULeaza Jernberg ngumphandi ozimeleyo oseRhawutini kunye nomcebisi kwidiplomacy.
“ISebe lezobudlelwane bamazwe ngamazwe nentsebenziswano, ngonozakuzaku boMzantsi Afrika ubukhulu becala, ithuku labo lakuqala yayikukuthi, ‘Kaloku, le ayamkelekanga.
Kwaye loo nto yayihlehlisiwe ngumongameli endicinga ukuba unenkxalabo malunga namahlakani kunye neRussia kwaye ijongeka njani le nto, utshilo uJernberg.
Ngoko nalapha eMzantsi Afrika, isikhundla soMzantsi Afrika sixabene kakhulu, nangaphakathi kurhulumente.
Amakhonkco oMzantsi Afrika kunye neRussia asuka ukusukela kwiminyaka yoo-1960 xa iSoviet Union yanika inkxaso kubalweli benkululeko ababechasene nocalucalulo.
Kwiminyaka eyalandelayo, abezopolitiko, kuquka abo bombutho olawulayo, iAfrican National Congress, bagcina ubuhlobo obusenyongweni neRassia.
Kungoko abahlalutyi besithi ayothusi into yokuba isiseko esikhokelwa ngowayesakuba ngumongameli uJacob Zuma sivakalise inkxaso kuVladimir Putin waseRussia.
URichard Calland yinjingalwazi yezomthetho kwiYunivesithi yaseKapa.
“U[Putin] ebenobudlelwane obusondeleyo nowayesakuba nguMongameli wethu, uJacob Zuma,” utshilo uCallland.
“Yayibubudlelwane borhwaphilizo.
Kwaphembelela into engekho mthethweni ekugqibeleni, inkundla yathi, ukuthengwa ngokungekho mthethweni kwamandla enyukliya aseRassia, okwayekiswa ziinkundla.
Kwaye ndinoloyiko lokuba oko kuphazamisana nezimo ezithile zezopolitiko eMzantsi Afrika.
Kodwa andikholelwa ukuba yayisisizathu esithe ngqo kwisikhundla esithathwe nguMzantsi Afrika.
Endaweni yoko, uCallland uthi, amagosa oMzantsi Afrika alandela nje umgangatho welizwe kwimilo yamazwe angaphandle.
“Ndibazi kakuhle kwaye ndinxibelelana kakhulu namagosa aphezulu ozakuzo eMzantsi Afrika, kwaye bangene nzulu kwelisiko lokungakhethi cala,” utshilo uCallland.
Ingxoxo yezopolitiko ligama labo eliphakathi, xa sesithetha.
Kwaye ndicinga ukuba kule, bebefuna ukugcina olu hlobo lwesikhundla esingakhethi cala ukuze bakhuthaze loo ngxoxo.
