Nokuba zithini na iinjongo, oko kushiye amazwe aseNtshona abambisene neiUkraine edanile, kwaye iingcaphephe zilumkisa ngelithi kusenokubakho ifuthe kuMzantsi Afrika kwixesha elizayo.
U-Ina Gouws ngumhlohli wenzululwazi yezopolitiko kwiYunivesithi yoMzantsi Afrika yaseFreyistata.
